00:15:25.980 --> 00:15:26.980
else.

00:15:26.980 --> 00:15:28.980
So you’re going to watch.

00:15:28.980 --> 00:15:31.870
This is over millions and millions of years.

00:15:31.870 --> 00:15:37.139
So the beauty of this is that you will never
get to see this, because we don’t live long

00:15:37.139 --> 00:15:38.139
