00:15:46.150 --> 00:15:54.160
So you’ve caught a chunk of things over
here on the far left-hand side.

00:15:54.160 --> 00:15:56.980
Everybody’s got a partner here.

00:15:56.980 --> 00:16:02.880
And this, this is how you figure out where
do stars come from?

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:04.940
How do stars evolve?

00:16:04.940 --> 00:16:07.290
How do they end up interacting with each other?

00:16:07.290 --> 00:16:09.410
