of years ago?

00:16:25.420 --> 00:16:27.950
Billions of years ago?

00:16:27.950 --> 00:16:30.199
This is the kind of stuff we get to figure
out now.

00:16:30.199 --> 00:16:36.200
It’s like forensic evidence that we didn’t
